    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "<smtcmp_block language=\"markdown\">\n## How to Use Templater with Your Daily Routine\n\n1. **Install Templater Plugin**\n   - Settings → Community Plugins → Browse → Search \"Templater\" → Install\n   - Enable and Hot Reload\n\n2. **Create Template Folder**\n   - Vault root → `Templates` → Create your template file\n   - Name it: `Daily Routine.md` (or any name)\n\n3. **Paste Template Content**\n   - Copy the full markdown from above into the template file\n\n4. **Insert Daily Note**\n   - Create new note → Settings → Daily Note → Choose location\n   - Settings → Templater → Insert daily note\n   - Use `{{date}}` for automatic date insertion\n   - Use `{{dateYYYY-MM-DD}}` for specific format\n\n5. **Customize**\n   - Edit task list and checkboxes to match your needs\n   - Add your own links and notes sections\n\nPro: Templater creates a note with the date in the filename automatically.\n</smtcmp_block>",
