      "content": "<smtcmp_block filename=\"dashboards/Professional Aesthetic Dashboard.mcss\" language=\"markdown\">\n---\ncss: true\ndataview: true\ntags: [dashboard]\n---\n\n<style>\n/* Aesthetic CSS */\n.dashboard {\n  max-width: 900px;\n  margin: auto;\n  font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f6fa 0%, #e4e6eb 100%);\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  padding: 40px;\n  box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\n\n/* Title Styling */\nh1 {\n  text-align: center;\n  font-weight: 300;\n  font-size: 2.2em;\n  background: linear-gradient(120deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);\n  -webkit-background-clip: text;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n  margin-bottom: 60px;\n  letter-spacing: 1px;\n}\n\n/* Section Cards */\n.card {\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\n  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  padding: 25px;\n  margin-bottom: 30px;\n  border-left: 4px solid #6a11cb;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n  transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-3px);\n  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);\n}\n\n/* Section Headers */\nh2 {\n  font-size: 1.4em;\n  background: linear-gradient(120deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);\n  -webkit-background-clip: text;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n  font-weight: 400;\n}\n\n/* Task Items */\n.task-list {\n  list-style: none;\n  padding: 0;\n}\n\n.task-item {\n  padding: 10px 15px;\n  margin: 5px 0;\n  background: rgba(106,17,203,0.05);\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  border-left: 3px solid #2575fc;\n  font-size: 0.95em;\n}\n\n/* Links */\na {\n  color: #6a11cb;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  font-weight: 500;\n}\n\n/* Tags */\n.tag {\n  background: rgba(106,17,203,0.1);\n  color: #6a11cb;\n  padding: 4px 12px;\n  border-radius: 50px;\n  font-size: 0.8em;\n  margin-right: 8px;\n}\n\n/* Date Display */\n.date-widget {\n  text-align: center;\n  font-size: 0.85em;\n  color: #888;\n  margin-bottom: 30px;\n}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"dashboard\">\n  <h1>🌸 Daily Aesthetic</h1>\n  <div class=\"date-widget\">\n    Today: {{dateYYYY-MM-DD}} | Week: {{dateYYYY-isoWeek}}\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h2>🍃 Morning Focus</h2>\n    <div class=\"tag\">#morning</div>\n    <p style=\"color: #666; font-style: italic;\">\"Start your day with intention\"</p>\n    <ul class=\"task-list\">\n      <li class=\"task-item\">\n        [ ] <span class=\"tag\">🌅</span> Wake up & hydrate\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"task-item\">\n        [ ] <span class=\"tag\">🧘</span> Meditation 10 min\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"task-item\">\n        [ ] <span class=\"tag\">📞</span> Morning review\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h2>💫 Tasks</h2>\n    <div class=\"tag\">#tasks</div>\n    ```dataview\n    TASK\n    where progress != 100\n    order by start desc\n    ```\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h2>📚 Notes</h2>\n    <div class=\"tag\">#notes</div>\n    ```dataview\n    LIST FROM #daily\n    | file.link | filename |\n    | --- | --- |\n    | [[Recent Note]] | \n    ```\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h2>🌙 Evening Reflection</h2>\n    <div class=\"tag\">#reflection</div>\n    <div style=\"background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;\">\n      <p style=\"color: #888; font-style: italic; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;\">\n        What went well today? <br>\n        <br>\n        What can improve?\n      </p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</smtcmp_block>",
